title: BabaBass3000
description:
Little room, big energy! Are you ready to get sweaty?

We're bringing out BabaBass3000 because we know you'll love his high-energy, no-nonsense dancefloor chaos—blending bouncy basslines, cheeky grooves, and fast-moving rhythms that hit hard and keep things playful. Expect big smiles, sweaty moments, and a set that refuses to slow down.

–––

All sales are final. Non-refundable.
No outside food & drinks allowed.

This event is 21+ years of age.
A valid government-issued ID required to enter.
